chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I would like to start off with something honest.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I wasn't given much, no blueprint, no safety net, but I wanted everything.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Not money first, not fame first, I wanted freedom.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I wanted meaning.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I wanted to build something that felt like mine.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And the only way to do that was to do it on my own.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Where I started, I didn't come from a world that taught me business.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I came from a world that taught me be safe, don't take risks, stick to what people expect.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: But I was never good at shrinking.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I had big ideas in a small space, big dreams in a quiet room.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And when you don't see anyone like you doing what you want to do, you either give up or

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: just become the first.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I chose the second.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: When browse became my language, browse wasn't just a trend for me.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: There were connections.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: People think browse are insignificant, but browse hold an expression.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Browse was never a trend for me.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: There were connections.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: How I watched people change in their posture, confidence, how they felt seen.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And how their confidence came back quietly.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And they can look in the mirror with their shoulders high.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: That's the confidence that made me grow.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: People didn't want to be transformed.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: They wanted to be recognized.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So I worked my work around individuality.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Not templates or not copying.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I wanted to have an existence or a meaning.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: What happens is clients go through illness, stress, hormones, trauma, and they lose their

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: hair and they lose familiarity.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: They lose themselves.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So when someone looks in the mirror and says, that's me again, and their shoulders soften,

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: their voice steadies, their presence changes, this is not beauty.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: This is reconnection.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And a reconnection changes how people move through the world.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And that's usually how people's beliefs turn into vision.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So doing business without a rule book is how my journey started.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I didn't know words like collaboration, PR, brand strategies.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I knew less help each other.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You know, you bring your people, I bring mine.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I'll help you today, you help me tomorrow.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: This is called being human.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Sometimes I worked less for what I should have.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Sometimes I trusted the wrong people.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Sometimes I lost money, real money.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Not mistakes on paper, but mistakes I paid for with my own savings, my own stress, my

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: own tears.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And many times I was told, you can't run a business.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You're not practical.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: This will fail.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Some of the voices were from strangers, friends, and even family.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: But I learned something important.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: People don't doubt your dreams because they're bad.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: They doubt them because they can't see themselves doing it.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And then why I traveled so much.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: People ask me, why are you always moving so much, traveling so much?

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: The truth is, at first this was my escape.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: When things got heavy, with no support, I felt missing, I would just take off.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: But when I felt misunderstood, I moved in unexpectedly the ways I wanted to without

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: having to do any marketing.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So when I traveled to these countries, I would find different cultures, different expectations,

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: different awarenesses, different faces.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I made amazing friends throughout all my traveling trips.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And this experience became my education.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: There was no business school, no mentor holding my hand, telling me to learn this way or the

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: hard way, through losses and long nights.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And then when things started working one day, I looked up and realized I'm fully booked.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And I was booked in months ahead.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And then it became years.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: But it wasn't because I was perfect.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: It was consistency.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I showed up, I learned, I failed, I fixed, I continued.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So no rule book, just resilience.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I'd like to do something with you guys together.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: If you can just raise your hands at some point in your life where you were told you can't

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: do, you can't do something, or something that you wanted to do but you didn't do.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I can't really see.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Yes, that's the room I want to talk to.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Okay, so I want to explain a little bit about a woman who deals with ADHD.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Someone with ADHD, my energy, my curiosity, my hyper focus, my excitement was seen too

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: much.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So I learned to shrink, to be wiser, to be more controlled, more acceptable.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And when you do that for long enough, something happens.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You either disappear or you rebel.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And I think I rebelled.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So then I stopped asking for permission to take up space.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And that once made me too much became my power.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: My speed, my creativity, my obsession to detail, inability to settle, all of this was

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: a learning journey to my entrepreneurial skills.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: ADHD didn't break me, it built me.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Once I stopped dimming my light to make others comfortable, everything changed.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: This superpower has now taught me to build myself slowly and honestly.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And this is how my training academy was born.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Not just a business idea, but a responsibility.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I didn't know the word entrepreneur when I was young, but apparently I was already practicing it.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: In secondary school, during lunch breaks, girls would start lining up for me, not for

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: food, not for gossip, but for brows.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I didn't know who I think I was.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I was just literally running the playground.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: One girl at a time.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And I was just shaping eyebrows for the whole school yard, like it was some sort of full-time job.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And then it got competitive.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Girls were so desperate that I started trading.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You want your brows done?

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You bring me candy.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You want your brows done?

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Help me in maths.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So I was like, running some operation.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: People were like, why are you queuing up for someone?

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Honestly, I looked like some new brow mafia kid in the playground, just taking on the

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: girls one by one.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: No badge, no title, just brows and bargaining power.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: At the time, I didn't even think I was clever.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I just thought I was busy.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I was enjoying what I was doing and making friends.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Now when I look back, I laugh and I think, wow, I really was a hustler when I didn't

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: even know what hustling meant.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: So I'd like to do some exercise, just a small one.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: I'd like you to all think of one thing that you've been wanting to do for a long time,

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: but feel scared to go after.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Don't say it, just feel it.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And I'll ask yourself, if no one judged you, would you have tried it?

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And that's exactly what I did.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You don't need permission to begin.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You don't need an applause to continue.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: And you don't need a perfect plan to move forward.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: You just need honesty and your efforts.

chunks.title: built-without-a-rulebook-suman-jalaf-tedxinvictus-school-amritsar-128-ytshorts.savetube.me
chunks.text: Success doesn't come from luck.

text: I would like to start off with something honest. I wasn't given much, no blueprint, no safety net, but I wanted everything. Not money first, not fame first, I wanted freedom. I wanted meaning. I wanted to build something that felt like mine. And the only way to do that was to do it on my own. Where I started, I didn't come from a world that taught me business. I came from a world that taught me be safe, don't take risks, stick to what people expect. But I was never good at shrinking. I had big ideas in a small space, big dreams in a quiet room. And when you don't see anyone like you doing what you want to do, you either give up or just become the first. I chose the second. When browse became my language, browse wasn't just a trend for me. There were connections. People think browse are insignificant, but browse hold an expression. Browse was never a trend for me. There were connections. How I watched people change in their posture, confidence, how they felt seen. And how their confidence came back quietly. And they can look in the mirror with their shoulders high. That's the confidence that made me grow. People didn't want to be transformed. They wanted to be recognized. So I worked my work around individuality. Not templates or not copying. I wanted to have an existence or a meaning. What happens is clients go through illness, stress, hormones, trauma, and they lose their hair and they lose familiarity. They lose themselves. So when someone looks in the mirror and says, that's me again, and their shoulders soften, their voice steadies, their presence changes, this is not beauty. This is reconnection. And a reconnection changes how people move through the world. And that's usually how people's beliefs turn into vision. So doing business without a rule book is how my journey started. I didn't know words like collaboration, PR, brand strategies. I knew less help each other. You know, you bring your people, I bring mine. I'll help you today, you help me tomorrow. This is called being human. Sometimes I worked less for what I should have. Sometimes I trusted the wrong people. Sometimes I lost money, real money. Not mistakes on paper, but mistakes I paid for with my own savings, my own stress, my own tears. And many times I was told, you can't run a business. You're not practical. This will fail. Some of the voices were from strangers, friends, and even family. But I learned something important. People don't doubt your dreams because they're bad. They doubt them because they can't see themselves doing it. And then why I traveled so much. People ask me, why are you always moving so much, traveling so much? The truth is, at first this was my escape. When things got heavy, with no support, I felt missing, I would just take off. But when I felt misunderstood, I moved in unexpectedly the ways I wanted to without having to do any marketing. So when I traveled to these countries, I would find different cultures, different expectations, different awarenesses, different faces. I made amazing friends throughout all my traveling trips. And this experience became my education. There was no business school, no mentor holding my hand, telling me to learn this way or the hard way, through losses and long nights. And then when things started working one day, I looked up and realized I'm fully booked. And I was booked in months ahead. And then it became years. But it wasn't because I was perfect. It was consistency. I showed up, I learned, I failed, I fixed, I continued. So no rule book, just resilience. I'd like to do something with you guys together. If you can just raise your hands at some point in your life where you were told you can't do, you can't do something, or something that you wanted to do but you didn't do. I can't really see. Yes, that's the room I want to talk to. Okay, so I want to explain a little bit about a woman who deals with ADHD. Someone with ADHD, my energy, my curiosity, my hyper focus, my excitement was seen too much. So I learned to shrink, to be wiser, to be more controlled, more acceptable. And when you do that for long enough, something happens. You either disappear or you rebel. And I think I rebelled. So then I stopped asking for permission to take up space. And that once made me too much became my power. My speed, my creativity, my obsession to detail, inability to settle, all of this was a learning journey to my entrepreneurial skills. ADHD didn't break me, it built me. Once I stopped dimming my light to make others comfortable, everything changed. This superpower has now taught me to build myself slowly and honestly. And this is how my training academy was born. Not just a business idea, but a responsibility. I didn't know the word entrepreneur when I was young, but apparently I was already practicing it. In secondary school, during lunch breaks, girls would start lining up for me, not for food, not for gossip, but for brows. I didn't know who I think I was. I was just literally running the playground. One girl at a time. And I was just shaping eyebrows for the whole school yard, like it was some sort of full-time job. And then it got competitive. Girls were so desperate that I started trading. You want your brows done? You bring me candy. You want your brows done? Help me in maths. So I was like, running some operation. People were like, why are you queuing up for someone? Honestly, I looked like some new brow mafia kid in the playground, just taking on the girls one by one. No badge, no title, just brows and bargaining power. At the time, I didn't even think I was clever. I just thought I was busy. I was enjoying what I was doing and making friends. Now when I look back, I laugh and I think, wow, I really was a hustler when I didn't even know what hustling meant. So I'd like to do some exercise, just a small one. I'd like you to all think of one thing that you've been wanting to do for a long time, but feel scared to go after. Don't say it, just feel it. And I'll ask yourself, if no one judged you, would you have tried it? And that's exactly what I did. You don't need permission to begin. You don't need an applause to continue. And you don't need a perfect plan to move forward. You just need honesty and your efforts. Success doesn't come from luck. It comes from choosing not to quit when quitting felt easier. When I wanted everything and I was willing to work for it, I didn't have the rule book, so I wrote one with mistakes. I didn't have guarantees. I built belief through action. I had unwavering work ethic and drive. And that's one thing I hope you take from tonight, is that you don't need to be ready. You just need to be willing. Willing to try, willing to fail, willing to continue, because the people who change their lives are not the ones who plan perfectly. They're the ones who start anyway. Thank you.
